    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much does a new boiler cost in Formby?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "A like-for-like combi boiler installation in Formby starts from £1,800 fully fitted. System boilers from £2,200. Regular boilers from £2,500. All prices include boiler, installation, controls, Benchmark and Gas Safe certificates. Free survey required. Many Formby homes need system boilers rather than combis for adequate hot water delivery — we confirm at the survey." } },
