        <strong style="color:var(--navy);display:block;margin-bottom:0.35rem;">Why system boilers are highlighted for Formby</strong>
        <p style="color:#1e40af;font-size:0.9rem;margin:0;">Most Formby properties have three or more bedrooms and at least two bathrooms. A standard 28kW combi boiler cannot provide adequate simultaneous hot water flow to multiple bathrooms. Fitting one leads to poor hot water pressure upstairs — one of the most common complaints we resolve in L37 after other installers have been. Our free survey confirms the right boiler type before we quote.</p>
